Rusty DeWees https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rusty_DeWees 0 Rusty DeWees (born November 15, 1960) is an American actor, producer and writer. He works regionally in Vermont, Off-Broadway, in television, and films. He is best known for his one-man comedy show, The Logger.
